                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-148-off819 t18270111-148-cd820"></join>, 5 pecks of coals, value 1s. 6d., and 3 pieces of wood, value 1s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18270111-148-victim1419" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Farrant
